position.call: In fours, circle left half-way and turn single left
Middle four circle right half-way and turn single right, while ends two-hand turn partner once around
All face neighbour, straight heys for four starting right shoulder
In fours, top and bottom, half right-hand star
Middle four left-hand star, while ends go single-file clockwise one quarter round to the sides of the set
